    narr:childCount "48"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "fd721ccf348291f1579109a8b073e09299ddd262" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of an [authoritative register](narr:StyleObs_Tone_Authoritative) within aswritten.ai, characterized by [active, agent-first voice](narr:StyleObs_ActiveVoice) and a rejection of epistemic hedging. The documentation style relies on [short, punchy declarative sentences](narr:StyleObs_ShortPunchyCadence) and [emphatic ALL-CAPS](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis) to signal architectural finality. A core corrective strain persists, where authors [explicitly retract prior conflations](narr:StyleObs_ConflatingProcessesRetraction) and use [block-quoted verbatim testimony](narr:StyleObs_BlockquoteCorrections) to ground claims in external evidence. The register is not exclusive to Scarlet; it is mirrored by [customer CTOs](narr:StyleObs_CustomerCTOGuardPullRequests_Imperative) and design collaborators, suggesting a shared idiolect of high-conviction, action-oriented communication. Epistemic rigor is maintained through [precise terminology](narr:StyleObs_EpistemologicalRegister) and [explicitly labeled conviction levels](narr:StyleObs_10), distinguishing between mere 'leanings' and 'settled decisions.' The documentation often employs [antithetical definitions](narr:StyleObs_9) ('not X but Y') to sharpen architectural boundaries, while [bold markdown](narr:StyleObs_BoldConviction) serves as a visual anchor for irreversible design commitments.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_10> ;
